  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Free school fees for displaced children in Burkina</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education is the basis of all development. Many children in Burkina Faso are unfortunately excluded from the education system because of security crises leading to the massive displacement of populations. The situation is catastrophic for displaced children aged 6 to 15. They find themselves forced into begging to survive. Global NEEED Burkina aims to ensure the reintegration of 500 children in the classes by covering all the costs relating to their schooling and their food.</narrative>
  </description>
